# hw definition file for processing by chibios_hwdef.py
# for FMUv3 hardware (ie. for Pixhawk1, Pixhawk2 cube, XUAV2.1 etc) with
# bi-directional dshot

# the bulk of the configuration lives in fmuv3-bdshot.inc so that it can
# be shared by boards which are based on it but do not share all of its
# hardware (eg. the presence of an IMU heater).
include fmuv3-bdshot.inc
